The paper discusses the security concerns related to edge computing and proposes a method for real-time lateral movement detection. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Science sub-category of Cryptography and Security (cs.CR). Additionally, the paper also mentions the use of artificial intelligence and network systems, which could place it in the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Networking and Internet Architecture (cs.NI), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing (cs.DC).
